Court Innovations Inc. – Online negotiation systems for courts and citizens.































Skip to content





Court Innovations Inc.









Online Case Resolution
Increasing access to justice for all citizens.










Matterhorn from Court Innovations allows courts to handle many high-volume infractions, disputes and outstanding warrants online
 



Learn More
Request Demo







Why courts are using Matterhorn



Convenience
Judge’s bench or citizen’s couch–resolve cases online anytime.


Efficiency
Reduce time and resources spent resolving cases.


Speed
Significantly faster case resolution and citizen payments.



Fairness
Neutral online platform fosters equity and consistency.


Collaborative
Courts, law enforcement, and citizens work together to reach resolution.


Access
Reduce barriers to access such as work, transportation and fear.






