 What are the benefits of online negotiation? Its free to search and see if you are eligible and you can do it at your convenience from home, work, school, using your phone, tablet or computer.  Traffic Ticket? You could get your charge changed to one with no or fewer driver's license points. And you can do it online rather than going to court.   Warrant? Resolve a fail-to-pay warrant without getting arrested or coming to court to see the judge. If you have a fail-to-appear warrant you can pay your bond online and receive a new court date.  How is it different online than in court? It's not. Your case is reviewed, and a final decision is made by the judge. Why does the court allow online case negotiation? We all make mistakes, and the court is there to listen to you and help you resolve your case. For Traffic cases, If you have a good driving record, the judge and police officer may be willing to give you a lesser charge that does not add points to your license.  For Warrant cases, the court has created this site to provide you clear instructions on how to take care of your obligations. 





